{"id":265651,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-山西村民土地被强占，因上访深夜被砍死/","date":"2012-11-28T09:45:46Z","modified":"2012-11-28T09:45:46Z","title":"维权网 | 山西村民土地被强占，因上访深夜被砍死（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钟剑报道）乔宝山是山西省临汾市尧都区贾得乡周家庄村民，生前曾因村民小组集体共有的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>余亩农用地被非法强占，五年未得到土地补偿款，而多次上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日，在洋州房地产开发有限公司非法施工的商品房建设工地，乔宝山先后两次在与开发商交涉时被歹徒殴打致伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时左右，开发商找人传话说给乔宝山一些钱，然后就别再上访了，开发商要求必须在当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点钟前回话，当即遭到乔宝山的严词拒绝。当天夜里，即</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2:30</span><span>分左右，乔宝山在家中被四名歹徒越墙而入持刀将其残忍砍死。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>乔宝山儿子乔永强强烈要求当地政府：一、对杀人凶手及幕后指使团伙从速缉拿归案，依法严惩；二、对黑社会性质的洋州房地产公司予以查处；三、责成相关职能部门依法保护村民合法权益，完成父亲遗愿；四、对事件涉及渎职单位：周家庄村党委、村委及相关单位从严惩处；五、希望媒体能对此事件公开曝光，督促事件得以尽快解决！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>然而，当地警方在很快抓住凶手后，却不再与被害人家属联系。乔永强告诉维权网信息员，目前此案居然交给尧都区纪委办，而且由贾得乡乡党委、周家庄村委会协助。这明显违反回避原则，简直就是交给主凶同伙协助办案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>乔永强联系电话</span><span> </span><span>：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13935728119</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-HYRfDTp2U0w/ULXTzBvcQ8I/AAAAAAAAUa0/KTr8FRseQss/s1600/125534332.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-HYRfDTp2U0w/ULXTzBvcQ8I/AAAAAAAAUa0/KTr8FRseQss/s1600/125534332.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7201543244687929585?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}